<document>
	<properties>
		<title>Moria2 and FEIDE</title>
		<author email="cato.olsen@uninett.no">Cato Olsen</author>
	</properties>
	<body>
		<section name="Moria2 and FEIDE">
            <p>
                <a href="http://www.feide.no">FEIDE</a> runs a Moria2
                installation providing an authentication solution primarily for
                Norwegian research and educational institutions. This chapter
                gives a quick overview of the details for this particular
                instance of Moria2.
            </p>
            
            <subsection name="Contact Points">
                <p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            You may contact the FEIDE administration on <a href="mailto:administrasjon@feide.no">administrasjon@feide.no</a>
                            to apply for your own service account on this
                            instance.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Any technical questions you might have can be sent
                            to <a href="mailto:moria-support@uninett.no">moria-support@uninett.no</a>.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
            </subsection>
            
            <subsection name="WSDL Locations">
                <p>
                    WSDLs for the Moria2 instance run by FEIDE can be found on
                    the following URLs, for various versions of the SOAP
                    interface.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Version</th>
                            <th>URL</th>
                            <th>Username to access WSDL</th>
                            <th>Password to access WSDL</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>v2.0</td>
                            <td><a href="https://login.feide.no/moria2/v2_0/Authentication?WSDL">https://login.feide.no/moria2/v2_0/Authentication?WSDL</a></td>
                            <td>demo_service</td>
                            <td>demo_service</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>v2.1</td>
                            <td><a href="https://login.feide.no/moria2/v2_1/Authentication?WSDL">https://login.feide.no/moria2/v2_1/Authentication?WSDL</a></td>
                            <td>demo_service</td>
                            <td>demo_service</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>v2.2</td>
                            <td><a href="https://login.feide.no/moria2/v2_2/Authentication?WSDL">https://login.feide.no/moria2/v2_2/Authentication?WSDL</a></td>
                            <td>demo_service</td>
                            <td>demo_service</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>
                    The differences between each version is described
                    in <a href="howto_service_wsdl.html">this</a> chapter.
                </p>
            </subsection>
            
            <subsection name="Available User Attributes">
                <p>
                    FEIDE defines a standard set of user attributes for use
                    within its Moria2 instance. The current attribute definition
                    can be found <a href="http://www.feide.no/dokumenter/feide-schema-current.html">here</a>.
                </p>
            </subsection>
            
            <subsection name="Available Internal Services">
                <p>
                    A number of Moria2-internal services may be accessed on
                    the following URLs.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Service</th>
                            <th>Description</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><a href="https://login.feide.no/moria2/Status">Status</a></td>
                            <td>System status page. Also shows connectivity status to authentication servers.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><a href="https://login.feide.no/moria2/Statistics">Statistics</a></td>
                            <td>Usage statistics for each service.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><a href="https://login.feide.no/moria2/Information">Information</a></td>
                            <td>Users may log on to review the information published about them through this Moria2 instance.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </p>
            </subsection>
			
		</section>
	</body>
